name: CIRenderInfo
desc: An encapsulation of a render task's timing, passes, and pixels processed.

items.name: var kernelExecutionTime: TimeInterval
items.desc: The amount of time a render spent executing kernels.

items.name: var passCount: Int
items.desc: The number of passes the render took.

items.name: var pixelsProcessed: Int
items.desc: The number of pixels the render produced executing kernels.
